        "heading": "Introduction",
        "body": "2.1 About {{COMPANY_NAME}}\n<Add a brief description of the company - here is a sample:\nSprinto is in the business of security compliances for cloud companies. Sprinto\u2019s platform helps\nmonitor entity-level risks and controls. Sprinto ensures compliance, healthy operational practices,\nand the ability to grow and scale with the needs of the market. Sprinto comes with framework-\nspecific workflows, policy templates and training modules for various security compliances. The\nSprinto platform seamlessly integrates with 100s of vendor tools in order to consolidate risk, map\nentity-level controls, and run fully-automated checks. >\n2.2 Vision and Goals\n<Add a brief description of the company\u2019s vision and goals - here is a sample:\nWe envision global leadership by redefining industry standards through innovation, excellence, and\ndedicated stakeholder commitment. Our mission is to deliver exceptional products and services\nthat empower customers, inspire teams, and positively impact communities. Guided by integrity\nand collaboration, we prioritize customer delight and operational excellence. Our focus on\ninnovation leadership drives market evolution, while empowering employees nurturing creativity\nand ownership. Sustainability and community engagement are integral to our growth strategy,\nensuring positive economic, social, and environmental impact. Through these values, we aspire to\nshape a brighter future for all stakeholders and contribute meaningfully to a better world. >\n3. {{COMPANY_NAME}}'s Approach to Information Security Management\n{{COMPANY_NAME}} places utmost importance on people, processes, and technology in conducting its activities.\nBy establishing and maintaining an Information Security Management System (ISMS), {{COMPANY_NAME}}\nenhances personnel's confidence, information security, and regulatory compliance. An ISMS\nreinforces confidentiality, integrity, and availability of information assets, elevating {{COMPANY_NAME}} among\ncompanies adhering to global Information Security Standards.\n3.1 Vision & Mission of Information Security Program\nFigure 1: Information Security Vision & Mission\n3.2 Approach to Information Security Management\n{{COMPANY_NAME}} has adopted a structured phased approach to Information Security management. The\napproach can be broadly classified into eight stages:\nDefining the scope\nRisk assessment\nSelection of control objectives\nDefine Statement of Applicability\nPreparation of ISMS documentation (inclusive of all relevant records) in line with ISMS\nframework\nReview of ISMS documentation\nImplementation of the ISMS; and\nPost-Implementation Monitoring and Review\nThe various stages of the preparatory phase and the implementation of the ISMS are depicted\nbelow in Figure 2:\nFigure 2: Information Security Management Approach"
