        "body": "Systematic risk assessments are important because they identify, prioritize, and help track the\ntreatment of risks to {{COMPANY_NAME}}\u2019s commitments to its customers and other stakeholders. The purpose of\nthis policy is to have a formalized risk assessment approach for risk identification, analysis, and\ntreatment."
